attr.title: SuperDrome Bugs
attr.desc: One day, Simon Pray -- a pest extinguisher living in Mexico, where for some reason pests are nowhere to be found -- receives a call from a luxurious mansion offering him a job. Something doesn't seem right, but Simon doesn't have time to think about it, he needs the money!. Join S.Pray and help him get rid of the pests!
attr.inst: You can download SuperDome Bugs for free at: https://pistachoduck.itch.io/superdrome-bugs. Download the SuperDromerBugs_Linux64.zip version and extract it, and place the SuperDromerBugs_Linux64.pck file in the gamedata directory.
